ProductInfo.Features:
This unlocked cell phone is compatible with GSM carriers like AT&T; and T-Mobile. Not all carrier features may be supported. It will not work with CDMA carriers like Verizon Wireless, Alltel and Sprint.
16GB of memory with microSD Slot for expandable memory up to 32GB
Windows 7.5 "Mango" Operating System; With Microsoft Office Mobile built in, you can operate on the go as seamlessly as you would at the office.
5MP Camera with auto-focus and LED flash.
Take your gaming experience on the road with the smartphone that lets you play games on Xbox LIVE.
ProductInfo.Name: Dell Venue Pro 16GB Unlocked GSM Slider Phone with Windows 7.5 OS, 4.1" AMOLED Touchscreen, QWERTY Keyboard, 5MP Camera, GPS, Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, FM Radio and microSD Slot - Black
